  <div id="text-content_c72d25a8-4380-4b97-a3f5-8c84e356c90e" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Discussions</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_discussion_topic" data-step-uuid="d2648954-913a-4127-8948-1e28bcd34e2a">
    <h2 id="open_discussion_topic" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Discussion</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/681/793/original/0c1f7023-8fa7-423e-9f54-a3d14118c22f.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
